  "texts": [
    "The HalluQA dataset encompasses 450 Chinese questions specifically crafted to test the hallucinatory behaviors of Chinese LLMs.",
    "These questions are classified into three types: misleading questions, highly misleading questions, and long-tail knowledge questions.",
    "During the assessment, GPT-4 is utilized to discern whether the models' responses demonstrate hallucination.",
    "• HaluEval (Li et al, 2023e).",
    "The HaluEval dataset functions as a benchmark for assessing hallucination in LLMs, containing 35K English evaluation samples."
  ],
